name: Soy Shots
description:
Just pop these Soy Melts into your oil burner and enjoy  :0)

Wild Frangapani
Just as the wild blooms of Hawaii would smell a delight to the nose

Coconut Cream
A lovely mix of Coconut Vanilla and Cream

Amber and White Musk
A rich, intoxicating fragrance with a melange of vanilla, citrus and a touch of coconut. Heart notes include heliotrope, coumarin and jasmine with a dry down of amber, patchouli, vanilla & musk. This is a soft, mysterious type scent.

Honeydew Melon
Let's go party with this marvelous melon scent kissed by green apples and fresh honeydew

Green Tea & Ginger
For thousands of years, Chinese emperors and royalty have indulged in white tea. It is only fired and dried, leaving its silver buds and select leaves fully intact - along with its delicately sweet yet herbal taste. Our fragrance adds a touch of jasmine to create a truly luxurious aroma

Mango and Papaya
Full of juice, like a melon, tropics. The sky is laughing. mango & Papaya are united, passionate. Pure fruits gone mad. 

Bird of Paradise
A sweet floral aroma with base notes of fresh fruits and vanilla.

Sweet Pea
An English garden that captures the very essence of sweet and floral elegance. Light and airy. 

French Pear
This variety of pear derive their name from the phrase, Doyenne du Comice, meaning, top of the show,as they are often celebrated as the best pear variety. Originating in France the fragrance is rich juicy and meltingly smooth. An amazing pear fragrance. 

Victorian Rose
A Fresh Crisp Rose with a great throw

Daisy Type
 This rendition begins with top notes of tangy lemon and jasmine; followed by middle notes of muguet lily, rose petals, African violet, and daylily;  sitting on base notes of cedarwood, patchouli, and musk.  

MoonLake Musk
A deep yet balanced musk that is well suited for either masculine or feminine products. Notes of fern and orris add to the musk flower and woody base notes. 

Frosted Snowdrops
A romantic musk and sandalwood background with the aroma of delicate winter flowers

Sinus Relief
Smells  very similar to the very popular Vicks Vapor Rub great for those times when we are a little snuffly :0)

Black Raspberry and Vanilla
 An enticing blend of blackberries and raspberries, with middle notes of white floral greenery, and bottom notes of musk and vanilla.  Highly requested fragrance!

Pink Magnolia
The aroma of the blooming petals of a magnolia tree

White Musk
A rendition of the well known Body Shop.......Great dupe this one

Mango and Papaya
  A tropical delight! You will fall in love with this fruity blend of ripened mango and juicy papaya.
